<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مِرْيَةٌ , وَمُرْيَةٌ وَاحِدٌ،<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> امْتِرَاءٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>